# Contextual Shopping Agent (POC)

Medusa + SvelteKit + Go Agent + pgvector

Goal:
Edge-style contextual shopping assistant enforcing:
- Budget constraints
- Sustainability threshold

Architecture:
- frontend (SvelteKit)
- agent (Go API)
- postgres (pgvector)
- medusa (catalog backend)

MVP Scope:
- Detect incomplete outfit mission
- Recommend missing slots
- Enforce eco_score + budget

